text: Jornada Lakes is a group of small ephemeral lakes in the upper part of the Jornada Draw in the Jornada Del Muerto basin in Sierra County, New Mexico. They lie along the Jornada Draw at an elevation of 4,688 feet / 1,429 meters. They are crossed by Upham Road between Aleman and Engle. == References == Category:Jornada del Muerto Category:Bodies of water of Sierra County, New Mexico Category:Lakes of New Mexico
